two buttons open?

361
00:17:14.825 --> 00:17:16.410
Let me guess.
Because you're cool?

362
00:17:16.452 --> 00:17:17.932
Damn right
because I'm cool.

363
00:17:18.494 --> 00:17:19.579
Because Daddy's cool.

364
00:17:19.621 --> 00:17:21.079
And Mommy is throwing him

365
00:17:21.080 --> 00:17:22.790
