391
00:18:19.932 --> 00:18:22.476
Uh. that's a no.

392
00:18:22.518 --> 00:18:24.561
Go shower. Be
back down in ten.

393
00:18:24.603 --> 00:18:26.146
-Go.
-I hate Chinese food.

394
00:18:26.188 --> 00:18:27.648
And I hate that attitude.

395
00:18:29.983 --> 00:18:32.402
-Gross.
-No. Cool.

396
