489
00:24:40.187 --> 00:24:41.771
Laugh or cry. right?

490
00:24:42.772 --> 00:24:44.524
How's he doin'?

491
00:24:44.566 --> 00:24:46.610
Oh... okay. Today...

492
00:24:46.651 --> 00:24:49.237
I... I don't wanna
