496
00:24:55.869 --> 00:24:59.789
Well. this man
can and does. no shit.

497
00:24:59.831 --> 00:25:01.291
I ache.

498
00:25:03.418 --> 00:25:05.253
If I was there right now...

499
00:25:06.922 --> 00:25:09.132
I'd be touching you
the way you like.

500
00:25:10.383 --> 00:25:14.387
